                    <p class="section-subtitle" style="color:rgba(2, 83, 107, 0.8);">With a passion for innovation and an unwavering focus on quality, our brand empowers fleets to achieve seamless, global supply chain success.</p>
                    <div class="row d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
